# Visualization Examples

## Heatmaps

* Row-scaled expression heatmaps
* Hierarchical clustering
* Treatment annotations
* Z-score normalization

### Color Scheme

| Color | Meaning           |
| ----- | ----------------- |
| Blue  | Low expression    |
| White | Medium expression |
| Red   | High expression   |

---

## PCA Plot

Used to visualize clustering of treated and control samples.

---

# Differential Expression Criteria

Genes are considered significantly differentially expressed if:

```text
Adjusted p-value (padj) < 0.05
AND
|log2FoldChange| > 1
```

